" < Switch Modes
""""""""""""""""""""""
" implemented via preference 'vintageous_i_escape_jj'
" inoremap jj <Esc>
" rnoremap jj <Esc>

vnoremap J <Esc>
" already built in: press v in visual mode to go back

""""""""""""""""""""""
" < Surround
""""""""""""""""""""""
" emulate some smarter punctuation bindings from Smarter MD Hotkeys
nnoremap <C-2> ysiw"
vnoremap <C-2> S"

nnoremap <C-5> ysiw]
vnoremap <C-5> iwoiwS]
nnoremap <C-6> ysiw]
vnoremap <C-6> iwoiwS]

nnoremap <C-8> ysiw)
vnoremap <C-8> iwoiwS)
nnoremap <C-9> ysiw)
vnoremap <C-9> iwoiwS)

""""""""""""""""""""""
" < Sorting
""""""""""""""""""""""
" [s]ort [s]election
vnoremap <leader>ss :'<,'>sort<CR>

" [s]ort [a]rray, if multi-line (+ remove duplicates)
nnoremap <leader>sa vi]:sort u<CR>

" [s]ort [g]lobally
nnoremap <leader>sg :sort<CR>

" [s]ort [p]aragraph
nnoremap <leader>sp vip:sort<CR>

""""""""""""""""""""""
" < Misc
""""""""""""""""""""""
" help
noremap ? :help nv<CR>

"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
" < NEOVINTAGEOUS LIMITATIONS
"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
" - Normal `map` (as opposed to noremap) is not supported
" - onoremap seems a little buggy, `onoremap i2 i"` blocks
"   any i command ðŸ™ˆ
" - as opposed to Obsdian, excommands (:help) need to be
"   confirmed with an <CR>
" - % does not work https://github.com/NeoVintageous/NeoVintageous/issues/825
" - macros are not saved to a register
" - gi does not work https://github.com/NeoVintageous/NeoVintageous/issues/810

" - Neovintageous does not allow for any insert mode modifications, these need
"   to be done in Sublime, with
"   "context": [{"key": "vi_insert_mode_aware"}]

